{"word":"G5524 - χορηγέω - chorēgéō - khor-ayg-eh'-o - Give","slug":"G5524","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χορηγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chorēgéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khor-ayg-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Give"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03B7;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - chore&#x0304;geo&#x0304;</b> - <i>khor-ayg-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5525\">G5525</a> and <a href=\"#/G71\">G71</a>; to be a <i>dance leader</i>, that is, (genitive case) to <i>furnish:</i> - give, minister."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5525\">G5525</a>"}]}